{"id": 2168, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今用社交软件，你都有哪些“反官方功能”的使用心得？", "description": "有些个系统功能啊，看上去贴心至极，以为我不知道其实都是新挤出来的广告位。（题图来自：Giphy）", "record_count": 19492, "comment_count": 32, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180208141203LJKAo7daF0PnQvqw.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-08T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3701, "title": "现如今用社交软件，你都有哪些“反官方功能”的使用心得？", "content": "如今在使用社交软件时，你都有哪些“反官方功能”的使用心得？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 264049, "content": "从不开自动推送，开了真正的提醒也会淹没在广告里", "image": "img/option/option/20180208141802Ty0Op1PM4rUsIqYl.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 264051, "content": "自动推荐的好友，从来不加", "image": "img/option/option/20180207224423p426ZtmvPYlXLRMd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 264057, "content": "定期查看自己关注的人，取关“被动关注”的营销号", "image": "img/option/option/20180207224643AwxQFacU79CjlZ4k.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 264060, "content": "软件替我自动勾选的内容，会条件反射点取消", "image": "img/option/option/20180207233739INYVmBXqAEiTO7RC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 264061, "content": "软件维持最低版本，能不升级就不升", "image": "img/option/option/20180208142231bfCikvWP3V8BpjgJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 264062, "content": "推荐感兴趣分类时直接跳过", "image": "img/option/option/20180207230029jZUvtqz3EfXl0SPK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 264064, "content": "基本不刷新首页，直接看特别关注或好友圈", "image": "img/option/option/20180208142025VI07cT5JA9BSPyWu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}